		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I really hate to dig up a post that is two years old (very noobish), however I would rather do this then start a new post with the exact same question.
<br />
<br />I have been brainstorming a NES project for quite a while and would like to incorporate wireless NES controllers.  I bought a couple of the "Acclaim wireless remotes" but found the ir pretty much useless.
<br />
<br />I've been a member of benheck.com for a while, but thought I would rather ask the question here seeing as people here seem a lot more knowledgeable when it comes to NES hardware and programming.
<br />
<br />I tried contacting the maker of the wii/gamecube version, but haven't received any response.  So how about the experts here, do you have any advice for me?
<br />
<br />ps.  Long time lurker, finally decided to sign up.

		

